These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, skiing, sailing, lacrosse
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, drawing, baking, singing
4 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, canasta, poker
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, canadian, nigerian, polish
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, alhambra, swisher, dunhill
 1. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 2. the person playing poker is between the person who's sport is parkour and the dunhill-smoker##2
 3. the argentine is the dunhill-smoker##1
 4. the canadian is on the left of the nigerian##1
 5. the baccarat-smoker is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person playing canasta##2
 6. the polish is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
 7. the alhambra-smoker is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
10. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Sport           | sailing | parkour   | lacrosse | skiing |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks      | drawing | baking              | singing |
| Game   | backgammon       | monopoly     | poker               | canasta    |
| Nationality           | canadian        | nigerian     | polish           | argentine       |
| Cigar     | alhambra | swisher     | baccarat                | dunhill      |

