.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, november, october, january
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, pall-mall, alhambra, dunhill
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, turquise, ivory, amber
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, roller, boat, tram
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, tulip, zinnia, iris
 1. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 2. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 3. the pall-mall-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person driving the roller##2
 4. the person who likes amber is the person who growsbellflower##1
 5. the person driving the boat is the pall-mall-smoker##1
 6. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
 7. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
 8. the person who growstulip is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
 9. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
10. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
11. the person who growsbellflower is the person who's birthday is in october##1
12. the person who's birthday is in september is the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Birthday          | october       | november      | september      | january      |
| Cigar           | dunhill | pall-mall | alhambra | cain |
| Color   | amber          | turquise       | ivory            | black      |
| Transport           | ship            | boat    | roller           | tram       |
| Flower         | bellflower        | tulip    | zinnia         | iris  |

