 6. the colonial house is between the person traveling to prague and the person watching horror movies##2
 7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 8. the gothic-revival house is the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's birthday is in april##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
