4 different games are played: canasta, scrabble, whist, backgammon
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, mystery, fantasy, thriller
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, spanish, australian, british
 1. the australian is the person who likes mauve##1
 2. the spanish is between the person playing canasta and the person playing scrabble##2
 3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 4. the person who growsaconite is the person watching time-travel movies##1
 5. the person playing scrabble is between the person watching time-travel movies and the indian##2
 6. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
 7. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 8. the person who growsorchid is the british##1
 9. the person who growsrose is between the spanish and the person playing whist##2
10. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left##1
11. the person who likes purple is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Flower      | daisy     | rose | aconite    | orchid          |
| Color          | chestnut | mauve     | lavender | purple         |
| Game   | whist    | scrabble       | backgammon         | canasta        |
| Movie-Genre         | thriller  | mystery     | time-travel     | fantasy |
| Nationality     | indian     | australian      | spanish   | british          |

