The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, baking, video-games, emeralding
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, emerald, blue, azure
 1. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who's hobby is emeralding##1
 2. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person traveling to miami and the person who likes blue##2
 3. the person traveling to paris is between the oliveros-smoker and the bolivar-smoker##2
 4. the person who likes apricot is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who growszinnia##1
 6. the person traveling to paris is the aristoff-smoker##1
 7. the person who likes azure is the oliveros-smoker##1
 8. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
 9. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
10. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person who's hobby is emeralding##1
11. the person who's hobby is emeralding is between the person who growszinnia and the person who likes azure##2
12. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who likes apricot and the aristoff-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar      | bolivar      | aristoff         | oliveros | ritmeester      |
| Flower           | zinnia | rose | dahlia | daffodil     |
| City   | prague         | paris          | nizza  | miami |
| Hobby         | video-games        | emeralding  | baking | singing   |
| Color     | emerald    | blue         | azure     | apricot     |

