.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, egyptian, british, french
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, ambient, classical, disco
House: cottage, modern, victorian, farmhouse
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, nurse, doctor, writer
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, skydiving, collecting, video-games
 1. the farmhouse house is between the doctor and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 2. the farmhouse house is on the right of the fan disco##1
 3. the nurse is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 4. the cottage house is on the far right##1
 5. the writer is on the right of the victorian house##1
 6. the nurse is on the right of the egyptian##1
 7. the mexican is the fan disco##1
 8. the fan ambient is on the right of the fan classical##1
 9. the french is on the left of the fan classical##1
10. the writer is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
11. the french is between the fan disco and the pilot##2

.:: Answer ::.
