.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, june, november, april
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, tennis, sailing, cricket
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, canadian, pakistani, italian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, balloon-flower, rose, iris
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, pall-mall, prince, bongani
 1. the pakistani is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the pakistani##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who growsiris and the italian##2
 4. the italian is the person who growsbellflower##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in june and the bongani-smoker##2
 6. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's sport is biathlon is the prince-smoker##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the nigerian##1
10. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |       4       |
| Birthday      | april    | june     | october        | november          |
| Sport         | cricket | tennis   | biathlon        | sailing |
| Nationality           | nigerian   | pakistani | italian | canadian      |
| Flower   | iris    | balloon-flower      | bellflower          | rose        |
| Cigar     | ritmeester  | pall-mall   | prince      | bongani           |

