.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, 7up, milk, fanta
House: futuristic, art-deco, tower, wooden
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, iris, lily, rose
4 different games are played: whist, go, chess, scrabble
City: hamburg, prague, nizza, paris
 1. the wooden house is the person who growsiris##1
 2. the person traveling to paris is between the person who growsrose and the person playing whist##2
 3. the person traveling to prague is between the person playing go and the person traveling to nizza##2
 4. the art-deco house is on the right of the wooden house##1
 5. the tower house is on the right of the person playing go##1
 6. the person playing go is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the wooden house##1
 8. the tower house is the person playing chess##1
 9. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is the person who growsazalea##1
11. the person who growsazalea is the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Beverage         | milk  | 7up | fanta | lemonade |
| House   | wooden      | art-deco   | tower      | futuristic    |
| Flower   | iris  | lily | rose        | azalea     |
| Game         | whist  | go  | chess     | scrabble      |
| City     | hamburg | paris      | prague   | nizza       |

 